  Getting Started

 Clone & Set Up

```bash
git clone https://github.com/panwarparth/quant_engine.git
cd quant_engine

# (Optional but recommended)
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate     # Windows
# source venv/bin/activate  # macOS/Linux

pip install -r requirements.txt
